title: Top candidate for Merkel´s successer Friedrich Merz tests positive for coronavirus

A Tennessee nurse recently went on an epic Coronavirus rant and it made our day. A woman who goes by the name "Emily Annette" posted a video to her YouTube channel going off about how many stupid people there are in the world. Emily…

meta_description: Friedrich Merz, a former Christian Democratic faction leader in the Bundestag, who is now seen as the most likely successor to Chancellor Angela Merkel, has revealed he has tested positive for coronavirus.
